        "its locale.\n" +
        "\n" +
        "August 15, 1945, close of Global War II! End of a world; dawn of\n" +
        "an enigmatic Atomic Age! The hermitage residents gathered in the\n" +
        "main hall for a prayer of thanksgiving. Heavenly Father, may never\n" +
        "it be again! Thy children go henceforth as brothers!\n" +
        "\n" +
        "Gone was the tension of war years; our spirits purred in the sun\n" +
        "of peace. I gazed happily at each of my American comrades.\n" +
        "\n" +
        "Lord, I thought gratefully, Thou hast given this monk a large\n" +
        "family!\n" +
        "\n" +
        "A small town on Coast Highway 101, Encinitas is 100 miles\n" +
        "south of Los Angeles, and 25 miles north of San Diego.\n" +
        "\n" +
        "I translate here the words of Guru Nanaks song:\n" +
        "\n" +
        " O God beautiful! O God beautiful!\n" +
        " In the forest, Thou art green,\n" +
        " In the mountain, Thou art high,\n" +
        " In the river, Thou art restless,\n" +
        " In the ocean, Thou art grave!\n" +
        " To the serviceful, Thou art service,\n" +
        " To the lover, Thou art love,\n" +
        " To the sorrowful, Thou art sympathy,\n" +
        " To the yogi, Thou art bliss!\n" +
        " O God beautiful! O God beautiful!\n" +
        " At Thy feet, O I do bow!\n" +
        "\n" +
        "\n" +
        "\n" +
        "\n" +
        "\n" +
        "\n" +
        "\n"
    var autoArray = autobiography.split(".");
